# Render/Railway dono is file ko samajhte hain.
# "release" phase = deploy se pehle ek baar chalta hai (migrations).
# "web" phase = actual server jo requests serve karta hai.
#
# IMPORTANT: `daphne` use kar rahe hain, `gunicorn` NAHI — gunicorn WSGI
# hai aur WebSockets support nahi karta. Daphne ASGI server hai, isi se
# Channels/WebSocket connections kaam karenge.

release: python manage.py migrate --noinput
web: daphne -b 0.0.0.0 -p $PORT core.asgi:application
